
1) This homework was written in vim.

2, 3, 4) For a web server, nginx was set up with MySQL and PHP.

# sudo apt-get install nginx
# sudo apt-get install mysql-server
# sudo mysql_secure_installation
# sudo apt-get install php7.0-fpm php7.0-mysql
# sudo vim /etc/nginx/sites-available/default
	- Added public IP as server_name
	- Allowed PHP scripts to be run with server
# sudo nginx -t
# sudo systemctl reload nginx
	- Added port forwarding to access web server
# cd /var/www/html/
# sudo mv index.nginx-debian.html index.php
	- Added <?php echo phpinfo(); ?> to index.php to test 

